entry.title: CVS stale lock removal: pdb2pqr
entry.summary:
Hi

I have a problem updating from the pdb2pqr project
since a lock file somehow was left in the repository.

Project: pdb2pqr

Error message:
cvs update: Updating pKa
cvs update: [13:45:08] waiting for czodro's lock in
/cvsroot/pdb2pqr/pdb2pqr/pKa

Can you pls remove the lock file?

Thanks

Jens
